### Health
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### 1.1 Google login with idToken
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idToken": "google_id_token"
}

### Refresh token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### Logout
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/logout

### Signup with mock social ID
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "GOOGLE",
  "socialId": "demo-google-user-1"
}

### 2.1 Set profile
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "JungTem",
  "factionId": 1
}

### 2.2 Get my profile
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Check nickname
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/check-nickname?nickname=JungTem
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### My books
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/me/books?page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### My sessions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/me/sessions?page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### My contributed libraries
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/me/libraries
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3.1 List factions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/factions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3.2 Create faction
POST http://localhost:3000/api/factions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "BlueDragon",
  "color": "#2196F3",
  "joinType": "FREE",
  "description": "독서를 사랑하는 진영"
}

### 4.1 Nearby libraries
GET http://localhost:3000/api/libraries?latitude=37.5665&longitude=126.9780&radius=5000
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4.2 Library detail
GET http://localhost:3000/api/libraries/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Nationwide libraries from Library Info API
GET http://localhost:3000/api/libraries/nationwide?pageNo=1&pageSize=100
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Nearby libraries from Kakao Local API
GET http://localhost:3000/api/libraries/nearby/search?latitude=37.5665&longitude=126.9780&radius=5000
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Geocode address with Kakao Local API
GET http://localhost:3000/api/libraries/geocode?address=서울특별시 중구 세종대로 110
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Sync libraries from Library Info API
POST http://localhost:3000/api/libraries/sync?pageNo=1&pageSize=30
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Resolve book by ISBN
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books/isbn/9788954682152
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Check book existence in a library
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books/isbn/9788954682152/exist?libCode=111000
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Recommended books
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books/recommendations?keyword=문학&pageNo=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 5.1 Start reading session
POST http://localhost:3000/api/sessions/start
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "libraryId": 1,
  "isbn": "9788954682152",
  "latitude": 37.5665,
  "longitude": 126.9780
}

### 5.2 Ping location
POST http://localhost:3000/api/sessions/ping
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": 1,
  "latitude": 37.5665,
  "longitude": 126.9780,
  "accuracyMeters": 15
}

### Submit verification material
POST http://localhost:3000/api/sessions/1/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startPage": 15,
  "endPage": 72,
  "submittedCoverImageUrl": "https://example.com/cover.jpg",
  "reviewText": "책을 읽고 인물의 선택과 갈등이 인상 깊었다. 특히 이야기의 전개가 주제와 연결되는 방식이 좋았다."
}

### 6.1 Verify book cover image
POST http://localhost:3000/api/verify/vision
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": 1,
  "submittedCoverImageUrl": "https://example.com/cover.jpg"
}

### 6.2 Verify review text
POST http://localhost:3000/api/verify/llm
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": 1,
  "reviewText": "책을 읽고 인물의 선택과 갈등이 인상 깊었다. 특히 이야기의 전개가 주제와 연결되는 방식이 좋았다."
}

### Get AI verification result
GET http://localhost:3000/api/verify/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 7 Complete reading session and grant reward - current route
POST http://localhost:3000/api/sessions/1/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 7 Complete reading session and grant reward - compatibility route
POST http://localhost:3000/api/sessions/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": 1,
  "startPage": 15,
  "endPage": 72
}

### 8.1 User ranking
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ranking/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 8.2 Faction ranking
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ranking/factions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
